<div class="pattern-center-blank">
</div>
<div class="pattern-center-sakura">
  <div class="pattern-attachment-img">
    <img src="<%= page.photos %>" src="<%- theme.lazyloadImg%>" data-src="<%= page.photos %>" class="lazyload" onerror="imgError(this,3)" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; pointer-events: none;">
  </div>
  <header class="pattern-header ">
    <h1 class="entry-title">
    友情链接</h1>
  </header>
</div>
<div id="content" class="site-content">
  <article class="post-item post-301 page type-page status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry">
    <% if (page.links) { %>
      <div class="links">
        <% (page.links||[]).forEach(function (group, index) { %>
		  <p></p>
		  <!-- 友链分类 -->
          <h3 class="link-title"><span class="fake-title"><%- group.group %></span></h3>
          <% if (group.desc) { %>
            <div class="link-description"><%- group.desc %></div>
          <% } %>
		  <!-- end -->
          <ul class="link-items fontSmooth">
            <% (group.items||[]).forEach(function (item) { %>
              <li class="link-item">
                <a class="link-item-inner effect-apollo" href="<%- item.url %>" title="<%- item.desc %>" target="_blank" rel="friend">
                  <img class="lazyload" onerror="imgError(this,1)" src="<%- theme.lazyloadImg%>" data-src="<%- item.img %>" src="<%- item.img %>" style="object-fit:cover">
                  <span class="sitename">
                  <%- item.name %></span>
                  <div class="linkdes">
                  <%- item.desc %></div>
                </a>
              </li>
            <% }) %>
          </ul>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    <% } %>
    <hr><br>
    <div class="links-content">
    <p>欢迎交换友链 ꉂ(ˊᗜˋ)</p>
      <p>
        请在下方留言告诉我你的：<br>
      <ol>
        <li>名称</li>
        <li>一句话介绍</li>
        <li>主页地址</li>
        <li>头像链接</li>
      </ol>
      <div class="entry-content">
      <p><b>Example：</b></p>
        <p>★ 名称: ctz</p>
        <p>★ 描述: 一只兼职蒟蒻OIer的死宅</p>
        <p>★ 网址: https://ctz45562.github.io</p>
        <p>★ 头像: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/ctz45562/cdn/avatar.jpg</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
    <%- partial('_partial/comment', {post: page})  %>
  </article>
</div>
